{"tid":2392622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(我屌你老母)NASA 延後Artemis 登月計劃的合約 登月計劃打上問號","createTime":"2021-02-03T02:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T05:12:23.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d44efcf4afd2e8e20009595170e84669d1c3ba01","tid":2392622,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特朗普政權下 NASA 力推在 2024 年重返月球的 Artemis 計劃，目前看起來能如期實現的可能性是愈來愈低了。<strong><span class=\"red\">原本預定二月底就要公佈的登月計劃合約廠商，被悄悄延後到了四月底，似乎預示著在拜登政權下，儘速返回月球已不再是急迫的第一優先項目。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n此次的登月計劃合約，主要是選定打造降落月球的系統的廠商，目前共有 Blue Origin、SpaceX 和 Dynetics 三間。當中 Blue Origin 是傳統的著陸艇、返航艇和轉移艇三部件組成，類似於阿波羅任務；SpaceX 當然就是直接端出了 Starship，而 Dynetics 則是一個配備「懸掛式」載人艙的著陸艇。本來 NASA 應該是要由三間公司剔除掉一間後，再給與剩餘的兩間進一步開發的經費，不過現在宣布需要「更多時間來評估」了。<br />\n<br />\n這其實是 NASA 長久以來一直都在面臨的問題 &mdash;&mdash; 每當政權轉移的時候，新政府對於預算的使用和側重都會有所調整，甚至發生極大的轉變。這在 SLS 開發過程中尤為明顯，讓其開發雖然並未中斷，但卻數度變更使用目的。 <strong><span class=\"red\">Artemis 是特朗普時代的NASA 署長Jim Bridenstine 極力推動的計劃，但隨著特朗普下台與Bridenstine 的離職，再加上拜登政府優先著重於疫情的控制與經濟的複蘇，Artemis 別說是原本極為激進的時程了，連是否能保住都難說。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就當下來說，計劃只是稍稍延後了兩個月，但除非新接任的NASA 署長同樣大力推動，且能獲得白宮經費上的支持，<strong><span class=\"red\">否則Artemis 恐怕是又要暫時被束之高閣，十年又十年了吧</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"0b77138830e28eaa605fcbe09fb5ab93160759c0","tid":2392622,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"BIDEN 唔搞太空計劃？"},{"pid":"ea1fcbb8e971fe903ff4cb356953d16d2850619f","tid":2392622,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:11:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/31/22258815/nasa-moon-lander-awards-biden-spacex-blue-origin-moonshot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2021%2F1%2F31%2F22258815%2Fnasa-moon-lander-awards-biden-spacex-blue-origin-moonshot&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=787bebe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/31/22258815/nasa-moon-lander-awards-biden-spacex-blue-origin-moonshot</a>"},{"pid":"8927d983c5172f89ee4f5f21b85ffdf6d02c3ca0","tid":2392622,"uid":295